short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Ebay dropshipping tool : Copy your customer shipping address from ebay and paste it on Aliexpress With only Two clicks

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Fullfill Order details  from Ebay to Aliexpress DropShipping Tool.Auto Fullfill Order From Ebay To Aliexpress
If you are dropshipping on Ebay thorough  Aliexpress platform this chrome extension  will help you save time for fullfill order details.
This extension will help you order quickly and accurately. 
First open your ebay order page, then click copy.
Then open your aliexpress product page and click paste.
This extension will make you save alot of time.
